data.description: This well cared for 3 bed 1/5 bath home in the heart of Seneca is ready for you! Settled on .46 aces in Cranberry School District, this beautiful home boasts custom cabinetry in the kitchen, first floor laundry, hardwood floors in living room, and charming front porch with great curb appeal. The heated 2 car garage opens onto a great private patio area for enjoying the fresh air.  Schedule a showing today!
